    "date": "2019-08-06T18:52:04Z",
    "text": "Modernizing Credit Opportunities Act\n\nThis bill provides that\u00a0an agreement between\u00a0an insured depository institution and a third-party service provider shall not affect (1) the\u00a0depository institution's role as\u00a0lender, or (2) the determination of the location of the depository institution."
